summary: I am an optimistic person, persistent in reaching my goals and I easily adapt myself to new environments. I have a lot of experience in multicultural environments and research, and have extensive knowledge about pedagogy, citizenship and gender. As a newcomer in the Netherlands, I have really wanted to integrate into society through work.
